text: Gunnar Hultgren (19 February 1902, Eskilstuna, Sweden - 13 February 1991, Uppsala, Sweden) was a Swedish bishop. He was active within the Church of Sweden. He was the Archbishop of Uppsala between 1958 and 1967. == References == Category:1902 births Category:1991 deaths Category:Archbishops of Uppsala
